{"tid":1425391,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警今晚嘅手法係為佢每日嘅記者會準備","createTime":"2019-08-06T18:02:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T18:41:28.000Z","uid":26130,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5d0d8e2c1ae9aaee60dc5e4808d3118ae29cf21c","tid":1425391,"uid":26130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:02:15.000Z","msg":"我覺得其實佢一早諗好點玩<br />\n如果唔係唔會捕住浸大個學生會長<br />\n有咩可能咁準時<br />\n一買電筒就拉<br />\n佢依家要日日記者會<br />\n要日日遣責<br />\n就係要鳩嚟激起民憤<br />\n日日都要你非法集結咁佢先有野講<br />\n<br />\n因為只有反政府嘅人先會知成件事幾on9<br />\n但藍絲廢老等人睇到嘅就係又有人搞事<br />\n要小心處理"},{"pid":"2fcdf2052467cb23fadc303513b6cb671bf7fc20","tid":1425391,"uid":26130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:02:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f48209ef358b4af59fc34f8553b97429a19b99ee","tid":1425391,"uid":26130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:03:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"333145c65a52d26fa92ec68e27abacf91588d5b4","tid":1425391,"uid":26130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:03:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"556e926c68bc80de4ad1ed0b431ca9ee83e364cf","tid":1425391,"uid":26130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:04:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9400eac1cec2f0e4007a11313f9a5f169e0e2c21","tid":1425391,"uid":26130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:04:16.000Z","msg":"十連"},{"pid":"3da428c971a96b61dd53e3f43917956a98cebdda","tid":1425391,"uid":127998,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:04:33.000Z","msg":"我又唔係咁睇 我覺得係班狗柒左"},{"pid":"684133c5871c4bf9e9682a6b500c7c8eaab5e1e6","tid":1425391,"uid":26130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:04:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fd5297034440a15f95150b82d90d52de251d91e0","tid":1425391,"uid":26130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3da428c971a96b61dd53e3f43917956a98cebdda","tid":1425391,"uid":127998,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score"